{"tid":948442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天富苑婦人抱BB危站40樓簷篷 消防正設法營救","createTime":"2018-12-20T05:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T07:09:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2642c821eeed0098b64d48a51ec7130ce109fa58","tid":948442,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181220/large/1545283116_4360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F1545283116_4360.jpg&h=61442ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婦人抱BB危站窗外簷篷。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<br />\n天水圍天富苑善富閣40樓一單位，中午12時08分，警方接報指一名女子抱着初生嬰兒，爬出窗外危站簷篷邊，婦人抱着嬰孩時站時坐，驚險萬分，救援人員已趕至現場，正游說婦人返回安全位置。消防飛將軍在對上一層樓戒備。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=0hdNa2H5pSPava9H49v2gI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=db8d8542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181220/59050882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59050882&d=0hdNa2H5pSPava9H49v2gI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2f19bcf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59050882&h=dbee2c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181220/59050882</a>"},{"pid":"62978f682497a618d2b3bc2009a62c078a084c1e","tid":948442,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:31:14.000Z","msg":"又係天水圍"},{"pid":"7a1d4d63dc90924ab